#include<iostream>

using namespace std;

long count[1000001];

int main()
{

   long t,n,i;
   cin>>t;

   while(t--)
   {

     cin>>n;

     count[n]++;

   }

   for(i=0;i<1000001;i++)
   {

     while(count[i]!=0)
     {

       cout<<i<<endl;

       count[i]--;

     }

   }

   return 0;

}
